some
  "Applies a function that returns an `Option` to each element of a list, collecting the non-`none`\nvalues.\n\n`O(|l|)`.\n\nExample:\n```lean example\n#eval [1, 2, 5, 2, 7, 7].filterMap fun x =>\n  if x > 2 then some (2 * x) else none\n```\n```output\n[10, 14, 14]\n```\n"
